dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. "Published under the superintendence of the Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge. (From the authorities of Colonel Leake and C.R. Cockerell ... ) " Map surrounded on three sides by "Panorama of Athens from the original drawing of C.R. Cockerell ... " and on fourth side by "Elevation of the northern side of the Acropolis, restored. Western view of the Acropolis, restored" / drawn by W.B. Clarke, archt. ; engraved by J. Henshall. Inset map: Acropolis of Athens. From: Maps of the Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge. London : Chapman and Hall ... , 1844.
dc_creator_sm: Society for the Diffusion of Useful Knowledge (Great Britain)
